          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              My guess is that you are stepping on toes and bruising some egos with your no-nonsense, completely logical way of doing things.<br /><br />I would say learn to schmooze a little.  Talk about sports for a little bit before telling someone you need to steal their people.  Acknowledge that someone's project has value before saying your's has priority.<br /><br />Stuff like that.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
