            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              So, when you have a new project idea, you don't get buy-in and support from your boss before you throw the idea out there? You don't proactively help other people and get favors returned later? You made some serious enemies how? Who is trashing you behind your back to management? Why did they get to management before you did? Do you help our peers? do you give your manager a heads up? do you help your manager pitch your idea to her manager?<br /><br />Are there perhaps things you are not telling us about your situation? <br /><br />pauli, if OP drags his derogatory view of making friends and trading favors into a new job, OP'll always be 'at the wrong company'.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
